ygData.messageBody:
Hehe guess you got em after I loged off. Its back
to camping guk for me, 50 hrs really sucked but that
item is worth it hehe ;) took me a looooong time to
find a group doing the gypsy lute in Mistmoore. It
even has better stats than mithril. ac20 +5sta +15(i
think)hp, so I end up with more ac and hp in the end. All
of the items have good stats and were better than
what I had before. So it is very very worth it for a
bard to do these quests.<br><br>Kaylin Danmor, 42(back
to camping soon to be 43) Bard, Minstrel of Norrath
on the Mithaniel Marr server<br><br>ps Trellan no
rush on the money =P
